## Detecting Your Framework

Check these files to determine the framework:

| File | Framework |
|---|---|
| `astro.config.*` | Astro |
| `next.config.*` | Next.js |
| `nuxt.config.*` | Nuxt |
| `vite.config.*` + `react-router` | Vite + React (SPA or Remix) |
| `app.config.*` + `@tanstack/react-start` | TanStack Start |
| `svelte.config.*` | SvelteKit |

